library(colorspace)
library(wesanderson)
df<-read_excel("AlmondYou.xlsx")
# Function to calculate the mean and the standard deviation of probiotics for each group
# data : a data frame
# varname : the name of a column containing the variable to be summariezed
# groupnames : vector of column names to be used asngrouping variables
##########################################################################
data_sum <- function(data,varname, groupnames){
  require(plyr)
  summary_func <- function(x, col){
    c(mean = mean(x[[col]], na.rm=TRUE),
      sd = sd(x[[col]], na.rm=TRUE))
  }
  data_sum<-ddply(data, groupnames, .fun=summary_func,
                  varname)
  data_sum <- rename(data_sum, c("mean" = varname))
  return(data_sum)
}
df1<- data_sum(df,varname="Bifidobacteria",groupnames =c( "Group","Week"))
## Loading required package: plyr
df1$weeks=as.factor(df1$Week) # Covert weeks to a factor variable
df2<- data_sum(df,varname="L.paracacei",groupnames =c( "Group","Week"))
df2$weeks=as.factor(df2$Week) # Covert weeks to a factor variable

# Line plot with error bars
# Graph of Bifidobacteria changes during storage time
p1<- ggplot(df1, aes(x=Week, y=Bifidobacteria, color=Group, shape=Group)) + 
  geom_line() +
  geom_point()+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks=seq(1,10,by=1))+
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin=Bifidobacteria-sd,ymax=Bifidobacteria+sd),width=.2,position=position_dodge(0.05))

print(p1)

p1+labs(title="Change of Bifidobacteria poplulation in almond yogurt alternative for control and treatment groups during 10 weeks storage ", x="Weeks", y = "Population of Bifidobacteria Log10 CFU/g")

# Graph of L.paracasei changes during storage time
library(ggplot2)
p2<- ggplot(df2, aes(x=Week, y=L.paracacei, color=Group, shape=Group)) + 
  geom_line() +
  geom_point()+
  scale_x_continuous(breaks=seq(1,10,by=1))+
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin=L.paracacei-sd,ymax=L.paracacei+sd),width=.2,position=position_dodge(0.05))

print(p2)

# change the color and theme
p2+labs(title="Change of L.paracacei poplulation in almond yogurt alternative for control and treatment groups during 10 weeks storage ", x="Weeks", y = "Population of L.paracacei Log10 CFU/g")+
  theme_classic()+
  scale_color_manual(values=c('#999999','#E69F00'))
